      {
        "name": "Magic Resistance",
        "text": "[name] has advantage on saving throws against spells and other magical effects."
      },
      {
        "name": "Limited Telepathy",
        "text": "[name] can magically communicate simple ideas, emotions, and images telepathically with any creature within 100 ft. of it that can understand a language."
      },
      {
        "name": "Variant: Familiar",
        "text": "[name] can serve another creature as a familiar, forming a magic, telepathic bond with that willing companion. While the two are bonded, the companion can sense what [name] senses as long as they are within 1 mile of each other. While [name] is within 10 feet of its companion, the companion shares [name]'s Magic Resistance trait. At any time and for any reason, [name] can end its service as a familiar, ending the telepathic bond."
      }
    ]
  },
